		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:2:{s:0:"";a:8:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"黄金的沉默与辉煌 ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"http://shihb.blog.sohu.com/260788736.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"http://shihb.blog.sohu.com/260788736.html#comment";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sat, 13 Apr 2013 12:40:04 +0800";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:13:"lastBuildDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 15 Apr 2013 23:19:18 +0800";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"评论";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:41:"http://shihb.blog.sohu.com/260788736.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43719:"<div style="line-height:160%;font-size:14px;"><div><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 26.25pt; "><b><span style="font-family: 宋体; "><font size="6">黄金的沉默与辉煌</font></span><span style="font-size: medium; "></span></b></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 5.25pt; "><b><span style="font-size: medium; ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; "><font size="5">时寒冰</font></span></b><span style="font-size: medium; "></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; "><span><font size="3">&nbsp;</font></span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">我们现在该如何看待黄金？黄金将走向哪里？我们需要对它有更理性的认识。</span><span></span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">本文将黄金分成两大块来看：一大块是实物黄金，一大块是以实物黄金为基础的各种衍生品（黄金衍生品属于金融衍生品的一种）。黄金市场衍生工具分为标准化的场内交易品种和非标准化的场外交易品种。标准化场内交易产品，主要品种包括黄金期货、黄金期权、黄金</span><span>ETF</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">（交易所交易黄金基金）等。非标准化场外交易主要包括黄金借贷、黄金凭证、黄金投资基金、黄金远期类产品（包括黄金远期、黄金掉期、远期利率协议）等。</span><span></span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; "><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">在国际黄金市场中，实物黄金的交易占比是比较小的，而黄金衍生品的占比近年来一直都在</span><span>90%</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">以上。</span></font><font face="宋体" size="3"><span style="line-height: 25px;">2010年7月，外管局曾对黄金储备做了明确表态：&ldquo;过去几年中国增加了400多吨的黄金储备，目前黄金储备已达到1054吨，即使再增加一倍，也仅能分散三四百亿美元的外汇储备投资，黄金储备占外汇储备的比重仅提高一两个百分点。&rdquo;显然，外管局认为黄金实物市场太小了。</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 21pt; "><span style="line-height: 160%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; text-indent: 21pt; ">因此，讨论黄金投资价值的时候，需要把两者分开。接下来将从衍生品与实物黄金两部分来谈黄金。</span></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">对于黄金衍生品的观点，我从</span><span>2005</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年起看多黄金，到</span><span>2011</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年</span><span>9</span><span style="font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">月为一个分水岭。</span><span></span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span>2011</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年</span><span>9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">月</span><span>4</span><span style="font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">日，我在《九月的棋局》一文中写道：&ldquo;</span><font face="楷体_GB2312">显然会加速资金向美国本土的回撤</font><span style="font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&rdquo;。&ldquo;下周起，美元将被走强&rdquo;（</span><font face="黑体">从<span>2011</span>年<span>9</span>月<span>5</span>日起，美元正式步入一个长达<span>4</span>到<span>6</span>年的上涨周期，此观点我在《时寒冰说：欧债真相警示中国》和多篇博文中反复强调。对于那些以短期走势看待长趋势的人，本人表示很无奈</font><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">）。</span><span></span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span>2011</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年</span><span>9</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">月</span><span>21</span><span style="font-family:
宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">日，我在《伯南克会说什么？》中写道：在美国轻松度过主权债评级下调危机，及欧债危机的恶化，强化了美元的霸主地位&hellip;&hellip;美联储比任何主体都更有动力和欲望推出</span><span>QE3</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">，同样是因为可以累积更多的现金，如果条件允许，伯南克绝不放过这样的机会。<b>美国轻松度过主权债评级下调危机后，黄金的投资价值阶段性削弱。美元与黄金的同步性问题，也明显变弱</b>&hellip;&hellip;无论</span><span>QE</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">是否推出，美元的趋势都只有一个，它不会因为</span><span>QE</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">而发生改变。会一直延续到美元&ldquo;被&rdquo;走强的阶段结束而走出独立趋势。</span><span></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><img src="http://1812.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2013/4/13/11/12/v8597_13ec55b5a16g2_blog.png" border="0" style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN: 0px auto 10px; TEXT-ALIGN: center" alt=""></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">美元步入强势上涨周期和黄金美元同步性的结束，意味着从衍生品角度来看，黄金投资魅力的减弱。而美国经济的复苏，意味着黄金避险功能的再次削弱。在此前一年一次的郑州讲座中，我曾做过专门的讲解，下图为课件摘录（下面的黑底白字部分皆为课件PPT）：</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;"><img src="http://1812.img.pp.sohu.com.cn/images/blog/2013/4/13/11/13/v8597_13ec55c2952g2_blog.png" border="0" style="DISPLAY: block; MARGIN: 0px auto 10px; TEXT-ALIGN: center" alt=""><br></span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">那么，黄金衍生品辉煌阶段的过去，意味着实物黄金保值价值的结束吗？</span><span></span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">不！它丝毫不减弱实物黄金的固有价值，尤其对于中国人而言！</span><span></span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">这似乎显得矛盾，但却是有内在因素所决定的。我们必须通过表象看到本质，在打压黄金的背后，暗含着对实物黄金的贪婪的掠夺和占有。其背后的意味深长非常值得考量。</span></font></p>

<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 160%; font-size: 14px; text-indent: 21pt; "><font size="3"><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">看看这则新闻：</span><span>2013</span><span style="font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
